title: [Maelstrom Bay, Bottom]
description: A rocky wall, strewn with dark green clumps of bladder rockweed, rises to the east.  A boulder the size of a hermit's hut is sunk into the sand of the bay floor.  Small, brightly- colored fish dart back and forth between the barnacle-covered boulder and the rockweed.
paths: Obvious exits: north, south, southwest, west, northwest, up
